# Floating Move Register

X-Form

* fmr FRT,FRB (Rc=0)
* fmr. FRT,FRB (Rc=0)

Pseudo-code:

    FRT <- FRB[0:63]

Special Registers Altered:

    CR1          (if Rc=1)

# Floating Absolute Value Register

X-Form

* fabs FRT,FRB (Rc=0)
* fabs. FRT,FRB (Rc=0)

Pseudo-code:

    FRT <- 0b0 || FRB[1:63]

Special Registers Altered:

    CR1          (if Rc=1)

# Floating Negative Absolute Value Register

X-Form

* fnabs FRT,FRB (Rc=0)
* fnabs. FRT,FRB (Rc=0)

Pseudo-code:

    FRT <- 0b1 || FRB[1:63]

Special Registers Altered:

    CR1          (if Rc=1)

